OL,3,CTeenagers sue Musk's xAI over Grok's
OL,4,Calleged pornographic imagery
OL,6,FThree teenagers are suing Elon Musk's
OL,7,Fartificial intelligence company, xAI,
OL,8,Fclaiming that the company allowed the
OL,9,Fcreation of sexually explicit imagery
OL,10,Fof them, therefore facilitating child
OL,11,Fpornography.
OL,13,FThe lawsuit against xAI was filed in a
OL,14,Ffederal California court on Monday.
OL,16,FThe young women from Tennessee, two of
OL,17,Fwhom are minors, say that xAI's
OL,18,Fartificial intelligence tool Grok was
OL,19,Fused to change clothed photographs of
OL,20,Fthem into nude imagery.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
