OL,3,CTeenagers sue Musk's xAI over Grok's
OL,4,Calleged pornographic imagery
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAccording to reports, lawyers for the
OL,12,Fteenagers said: "xAI ` and its founder
OL,13,FElon Musk ` saw a business
OL,14,Fopportunity."
OL,16,FThey added: "They knew Grok could
OL,17,Fproduce such results, including by
OL,18,Fusing the images and videos of
OL,19,Fchildren, and publicly released it
OL,20,Fanyway."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
