OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773778273
OL,3,CTeenagers sue Musk's xAI over Grok's
OL,4,Calleged pornographic imagery
OL,6,F"Their lives have been shattered by
OL,7,Fthe devastating loss of privacy,
OL,8,Fdignity, and personal safety," they
OL,9,Fsaid in their complaint.
OL,11,FThis is the first lawsuit to be filed
OL,12,Fby minors, with the teenagers involved
OL,13,Fremaining anonymous for privacy
OL,14,Freasons.
OL,16,FOne of the young women said she
OL,17,Fdiscovered the photographs after she
OL,18,Fwas sent an anonymous direct message
OL,19,Fon Instagram telling her her high
OL,20,Fschool yearbook photo had been edited,
OL,21,Fnow showing her in explicit ways.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
