OL,3,CTeenagers sue Musk's xAI over Grok's
OL,4,Calleged pornographic imagery
OL,6,FThe other teens found sexually
OL,7,Fexplicit imagery of themselves online,
OL,8,Falso created by Grok.
OL,10,FThe generative AI bot has been
OL,11,Finvolved in an ongoing deepfake porn
OL,12,Fscandal. Last year, xAI introduced a
OL,13,Fnew Grok feature, "spicy mode",
OL,14,Fallowing users to generate fake sexual
OL,15,Fimages.
OL,17,FThe mode was able to "undress" real
OL,18,Fpeople, using images from the internet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
