OL,3,CTeenagers sue Musk's xAI over Grok's
OL,4,Calleged pornographic imagery
OL,6,FAccording to the Centre for Counting
OL,7,FDigital Hate (CCDH), "Grok generated
OL,8,Fan estimated 3 million sexualized
OL,9,Fimages, including 23,000 of children"
OL,10,Fbased on their sampling.
OL,12,FEarlier this year, Musk wrote in a
OL,13,Fpost on X: "Obviously, Grok does not
OL,14,Fspontaneously generate images, it does
OL,15,Fso only according to user requests."
OL,17,FLater, X said it had "implemented
OL,18,Ftechnological measures to prevent the
OL,19,FGrok account from allowing the editing
OL,20,Fof images of real people in revealing
OL,21,Fclothing such as bikinis".
