OL,6,FOfcom and the European Commission
OL,7,Flaunched investigations following
OL,8,Fpublic concern.
OL,10,FITV News approached xAI for a comment
OL,11,Fon the recent lawsuit, but it did not
OL,12,Fimmediately respond.
